    <item>
      <title>股票买家电力风险集会随着债券的打击：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/asian-stocks-under-pressure-as-uncertainty-rises-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贸易商抢购了受虐的科技股，股票集会，而迹象表明，美国关税的目标比预期的要降低了安全性的胃口。债券倒下了。唐纳德·特朗普总统表示，他将向委内瑞拉购买原油和天然气的国家征收25％的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/asian-stocks-under-pressure-as-uncertainty-rises-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 22:28:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
